item.title: April Gobabygo summit
item.dc:creator: Mark
item.description:
I had to ask if they were having one and got a third hand invite. Not sure if the $4,000 air flights and $1000 hotel costs are worth it. I think they may be some what dis organised through this whole thing growing way faster than anyone had planned or given much thought to. But I would like to see what everyone else does as I feel we could learn a huge amount.
